{C}(G_2)$ are stably $\\mathbb{C}$-isomorphic with\n$Br_{nr}(\\mathbb{C}(G_i))\\simeq C_2$. Explicit structures of non-rational\nfields $\\mathbb{C}(G)$ are given for each cases including also the case\n$\\Phi_{30}$ with $Br_{nr}(\\mathbb{C}(G))\\simeq C_2\\times C_2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Apr 2014 16:45:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-02"}
