/VM with the viscosity and\nconductivity for various ionic liquids. Correlation between the free volume and\nthe molecular volume of ionic liquids were explained by a schematic free volume\nmodel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Apr 2014 19:44:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-02"}
