\ndirectly provide for $\\beta=2$ the full statistics of particle-number\nfluctuations at zero temperature of 1d spinless fermions in a harmonic trap.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Apr 2014 14:44:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Jun 2014 13:30:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-30"}
